      <prompt>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <div>Which clotting factor is activated when there is trauma to the blood or exposure of the blood to collagen from a traumatized blood vessel wall?</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div>Which clotting factor activates factor IX to IXa and also activates Factor VIII, calcium and phospholipid?</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div>Which clotting factor activates XIII to XIIIa?</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div>Which factor activates X to Xa (along with tissue factor and calcium)?</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div>Which factor, along with Factor V and activated platelets, converts prothrombin to thrombin?</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </prompt>
      <simpleChoice identifier="CHOICE_000">
        <div>Factor VIIa</div>
      </simpleChoice>
